tool_description: Google Search API. Search the world’s information, including webpages, related keywords and more.
name: Google Search_v2
title: Google Search

api_list.name: search

parameters.name: query
parameters.description:
Search query. You can use Google Search parameters.

e.g. adele site:youtube.com
e.g. harry potter filetype:pdf
e.g. inurl:store
e.g. ronaldo -cristiano

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: Max results number. Max recommended value is 300

parameters.name: related_keywords
parameters.description:
Shows related keywords. Default: false

Entering true, increases API latency

utterances.utterance: Find the latest news articles about climate change.
Search for PDF documents related to machine learning.
Look up YouTube videos of Adele.
Find webpages with 'store' in the URL.
Search for information about Ronaldo excluding Cristiano.
Get the top 20 results for 'quantum computing'.
Search for 'solar energy' and show related keywords.
Find the top 50 results for 'blockchain technology'.
Search for 'Python programming' tutorials on YouTube.
